  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Apartments you couldn't get.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You just were in the room where you were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And more food, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was all at the same time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how they were connected, because I know the Zionist group and I know the Communist group were not really the best of friends at one time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then I guess in the ghetto, they connected.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They must've been in the existence already in Prague and in Brunn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think they did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know personally, but I think they did from Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think they did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that was in the making.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in the making of, but never got to it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because there were too many transport going already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Couldn't go ahead.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Too many young people left, and the oldest-- oldest ones were behind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The old ones were left behind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what it is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like I told you, we had that wall, which was normally [INTERPOSING VOICES] built around [? garrison ?] town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I'm not sure, but I think it was like about 7:00, [BACKROUND NOISE] 8:00 o'clock in the evening, something on that order.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they also had a-- a countdown every-- wherever you lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What room you were in, or in a home, or in a building, or-- or wherever people lived together, there was a countdown every day.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They knew there were so and so many people in that building, and there had to be so and so many people in that building, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- Someone would come around to check how many people?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That I know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were marriages in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What they called ghetto weddings.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
